Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到無聊的視察終於要結束了 我就感覺很清靜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你還真會做表面功夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------------Staff------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死囚樂園好也罷壞也罷 都是這個社會的縮影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.42,0:00:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是如實模仿社會系統所製造出的微型世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.46,0:00:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的音樂背後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有著不堪入目的爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓鮮血四濺的不就是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過是在提供而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給予這幫瘋子寶貴的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:00:59.16,Logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(230,200)}曙光社字幕組\NSGS Fansub
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:03.72,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Strict control of reason and reality
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:08.18,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Cut myself and scream for their insanity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:12.48,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Wake up into this nightmare that will never end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.52,0:01:17.28,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}The main attraction of this twisted master plan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.93,0:01:34.28,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I will be your deadman
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.35,0:01:38.66,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}With nothing but this blood on my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:43.10,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stuck in your Wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.15,0:01:47.43,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I wanna make you bleed just like me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:51.95,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}So make me your deadman
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:56.23,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}With only poison in my veins
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:02:00.64,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stuck in your Wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.95,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stuck in a battle I have to make
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:05.72,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm gonna make you bleed like me
