Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.94,0:02:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.73,0:02:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本那麼溫柔 那麼強大的人卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是那樣 其實他很軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…沒能保護好他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為自己能讓他從這個世界逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 他殺了許多自己人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦角?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他很弱?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 只能沉默不語 或隨之瘋狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 為什麼都還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做這種事情我也不會原諒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手吧 風
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想讓丸太你來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快閃開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 這種程度白是不會痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.57,0:03:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那麼弱 為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋丸太 快閃開吧 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊 風
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣 看著朋友被紅衣男殺掉 渣到根了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 「沒有時間去考慮復仇」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你對我說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前提是「只要還有希望」 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子…我的光芒 已經沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡只有黑暗 和憎恨!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 你會說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風的痛苦 其實我無法體會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是死了的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:05:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被殺掉的傢伙再也回不來了 這種悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞和懊悔 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣 風的周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不全是光芒在閃耀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你一直都低著頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你連這種事都搞不清楚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風的身邊不是有很多光芒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的 光芒…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我的希望已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的光 至今還在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 雖然做了很多過分的蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想失去她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我很弱 即使這是個瘋狂的地方 也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 會保護我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貧血? ?不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了 身體…麻痺了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 最後一次吃「Candy」是什麼時候來著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 「貓頭鷹」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我挺起腰桿啊 風
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我們的老大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那鈴聲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表我也有著重要的夥伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 唐子 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要哭要贖罪 等逃出這裡後再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別泡我的修羅 你這混蛋女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.38,0:08:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別大呼小叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我難得讓她得到了救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一個想要見見自己孩子的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一個一心想要幫助別人的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜 生 ⑽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 你會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不起作用?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧 想我救你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我避開了心臟和肺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過應該刺進骨頭裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人深愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:10:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由你來把她送上西天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是她最好的救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒說錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是憎恨一切 用殺戮來救贖的修羅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過是個軟弱的人類罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死 怎會是救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的救贖 就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 為了自由而並肩作戰的同伴就在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是認真的吧 「貓頭鷹」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘋掉的你很美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺戮的身影也很迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾愛著你呦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要變回那個無法普度眾生的混帳偽君子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就由我來將你救贖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊 弦角…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 弦角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈施的時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南無阿彌陀佛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又到鎮上和人打架了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原以為你是個溫馴穩重的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡因只會招致惡果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不恨他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個扭曲的現世上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懦弱地不幸地 陷於無上的愚蠢之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法師大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普度眾生的方法是否存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹悟真的就能逃脫生老病死麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼佛祖大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不知道什麼是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻認定死亡是痛苦的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 救救 我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,益信 午安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 法師大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於明白 如何普度眾生了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜寂就是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平也是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安寧即是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執枉也是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善美都是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹悟也是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案就是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡才是救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又吉 晴美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都是掙扎著想逃出去的「Deadman」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能望著外界死去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多好的墳墓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒素蔓延 很痛苦吧 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個地下就是你們的墳墓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在恐懼中 僵化狂暴地活著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身沾滿了著罪和五臟六腑而死去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才能得到救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我這個超級和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:32.51,Float,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(729,653)}Grateful Dead
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來賜予你們拯救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛空一閃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:53.70,Float,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(642,653)}Invisible Black
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點程度就裂開了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是很脆弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 他們必須被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 必須要哭泣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我 什麼都做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快掛掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐小貓還是做掉比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到被救贖之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直拯救下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐懼 壓抑 背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕望 侮辱 後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷 痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘋狂 痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會從fucking的世界中拯救你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫的 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開 白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次 輪到我當Ace Man了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混賬和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的大家都懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只要有朋友在 就有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰有閒工夫找死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起下地獄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我的救贖麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十嵐 你在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎 已經用不著了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣 就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然充滿了希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:19:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好溫暖的雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會出現美麗的彩虹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃閃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:19:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 你不出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說過很想出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能丟下朋友不管的 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 之前打了你 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我 還做了過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 已經不痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還一起看到了閃閃輪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.93,0:20:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後有機會一起坐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 還有哪裡痛麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是糖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:20:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這件事以後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 以後就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.66,0:21:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦角他們居然這麼不頂用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉色很不好啊 創辦人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是被死囚逃獄了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.94,0:21:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢 蒔名小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的管轄區內沒有少哪一個囚犯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是還不習慣當所長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒經過交接 他突然就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 我的管轄區內沒有少人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5580號五十嵐丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和9061號鷹見羊都回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都受了重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這11天裡 他們去了哪裡 幹了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就去審問清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看情況也許會上點傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒你的風格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你喜歡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和往常一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.07,0:22:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會聽到趣事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.63,0:22:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要揉肩膀麼 蒔名長官
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.44,0:22:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人選定好了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.17,0:22:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從創始人名簿上的一般犯人之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選出了一名最合適人選
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.47,0:22:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 要行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子果然很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.86,0:22:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有那麼強的「罪之枝」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.69,0:22:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼味道的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做盡壞事的啄木鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也在不停地啄 森林已是千瘡百孔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.91,0:23:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發怒了的森林之神 將它的喙變成了毒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.70,0:23:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦惱的啄木鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.43,0:23:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巢穴染上了毒 食物也染上了毒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友碰到它 全都相繼地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷的啄木鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.51,0:23:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩有毒的淚水閃爍著光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.56,0:23:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.40,0:23:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.20,0:24:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是丸太的媽媽寫的歌嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.97,0:24:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很懷念 但還是別唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.49,0:24:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.72,0:24:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候…紅衣男也唱了這首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.75,0:24:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那個傢伙 為什麼會知道這首歌呢
